      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and restoration fans! This vehicle is in poor condition and is ready for someone with a vision to bring it back to its former glory. While it needs significant mechanical and cosmetic work, it offers a wonderful foundation for a rewarding project. Grab this opportunity to build your dream car from the ground up at a great price!",
